This paper belongs to the sub-category of Case Based AI. 

Explanation: The paper focuses on developing an adaptive similarity assessment method for case-based explanation. It discusses the use of case-based reasoning (CBR) and how it can be improved by incorporating adaptive similarity assessment. The paper does not mention any other sub-categories of AI such as Genetic Algorithms, Neural Networks, Probabilistic Methods, Reinforcement Learning, Rule Learning, or Theory.
